Package: clinicaldigitaltwin
Title: Clinical Digital Twin Monitoring System (Hackathon MVP)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Hackathon", "Team", , "team@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A hackathon prototype that lets clinicians visualize synthetic
    patient vitals/activity data and run "what-if" simulations on statistical
    digital twins to estimate fall risk. All patient data is synthetic. Not
    for clinical use.
